- **Pause / resume:** [Durable pending state, authenticated decision, proposal binding, revalidation, and idempotent resume]
- **Kill switch:** [How the owner stops execution or recurrence]

## Lifecycle

- **Promotion:** [Evidence required to move from pilot to review-only or automated]
